author: ekoneil
msg: Work on the Ant targets used to deploy NetUI into a webapp.
This breaks the deployment of NetUI out of the test/ant/buildWebapp.xml and into a deployNetuI.xml Ant file; this will enable the buildWebapp.xml file to be used in the distribution.
Update build files that make use of this and change references for "deploy.netui" in buildWebapp.xml to "deploy.netui" in ${deployNetui.ant} which is defined in beehive.properties.
Also add "deploy.netui" and "undeploy.netui" targets in $BEEHIVE_HOME/netui/build.xml which can be called externally from the NetUI build.
